    (Note (NoteNumber 276)
        (NoteText "The interpretation of the 32 bits defining the entity appearance is to be derived from the federation agreements, which could refer to the entity appearance record as defined in SISO-REF-010. The reason that this has not been split out into separate fields (as has been done for the subclasses of BaseEntity) is the difficulty of providing an efficient manner of defining an array of such appearance fields.")
    )
